<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>rclone -v serve ftp --addr 0.0.0.0:2121 --user ftp --pass ftp .
# -v is for verbose
# port 2121 is so the root is not needed for binding
# . is for this dir
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Rclone is a go app <a href="https://rclone.org/downloads">https://rclone.org/downloads/</a>.</p>
